      As  MP3  CD  ripper - extract CD tracks to MP3, WAVE, OGG, FLAC, APE.
      With  the  friendly  interface, you will complete CD ripping within a
      few  minutes.  Provide  supports  from CDDB. CDDB is a FreeDB Server,
      where  information  (title,  genre,  etc.) of tens of thousands of CD
      albums   is   stored.   Without  your  work,  Arial  CD  Ripper  will
      automatically  search CDDB and find the relevant information for your
      CD.    As    Audio   Converter:   Convert   audio   formats   between
      mp3,wav,ogg,flac  and  ape  with as simple as a click.It is the ideal
      all-in-one  tool  for  converting  batches  of  MP3  into  WAV for CD
      burning.It&#039;s  also  great for converting your favorite old collection
      of  WAV  into the space-saving condensed MP3 format As Id3 Tager. Id3
      Tag records the information of the songs in formats such as MP3. Each
      song  is  automatically tagged at the time you transform the CD files
      into  MP3.  In  addition,  Arial  CD  Ripper also provides the unique
      compilation  function  from  ID3  Tag,  by which you can edit all MP3
      files   in  your  hard  disk.  Smart  and  Convenient  Settings:  Has
      convenient  and  smart  output  settings  (output  directory,  output
      format,  etc),setting  setup  wizard can help you finish the settings
      without  difficulty.  If  you are not so familiar with music formats,
      please use our default settings, Arial CD Ripper has already selected
      optimal  settings  for  you  as  default. With uncluttered and pretty
      interface,  Arial  CD  Ripper  is a very easy to use tool.With superb
      output  quality and high speed conversion,you can enjoy your favorite
      music anytime and anywhere by saving the output MP3 music in your MP3
      player.
